Package: tabstats
Type: Package
Title: Helpers for displaying tables
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        "Joshua", "Marie",
        email = "joshua.marie.k@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
    )
Maintainer: Joshua Marie <joshua.marie.k@gmail.com>
Description: A lightweight package that consists the collection of functions to print 
    the data in a table format within command line. This includes a default table, 
    contingency table, correlation matrix, and a summary table in 2 columns form.
